{
 "name": "RPlog_Selene_Day_s_Wookiee_Hunt",
 "title": "Selene Day's Wookiee Hunt",
 "summary": "As a centerpiece of the Selene Day festivities, Moff Marx stages a brutal \"Hunt of the Wookiee\" in which Imperial hunters chase a tormented, caged Wookiee released into the planet's radioactive, frozen wastelands. Among the hunters are Admiral Danik Kreldin and his comrades Sandor Woden and Darenak Alesis, the disguised Moff Claven, the kitchen-trained Lauranne Tremichall, and the cavalier executive Xerxes Kherzen with his recording droid. The terrified Wookiee flees through corpse-strewn ruins seeking shelter, but Sandor's sharp eyes spot it and the hunters converge on the residential district. A chaotic firefight erupts when Claven stumbles into the creature's hiding place; sniper fire, stun bolts, and Kreldin's bayonet charge finally cut the Wookiee down, and Sandor delivers the killing shot to claim victory and an invitation to meet Moff Marx.",
